<lb n="0284c11" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><note n="0284005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】三十帖策子第二十七，【乙】同第二十帖，【丙】黃蘗版淨嚴等校訂加筆本塚本賢曉氏藏，【丁】縮冊大藏經</note><cb:jhead>金剛頂<note n="0284006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經瑜伽＝瑜伽經【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0284006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經瑜伽＝瑜伽經【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0284006"><lem wit="【大】">經瑜伽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】">瑜伽經</rdg></app>十八會指歸<note n="0284007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【三】【宮】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0284007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一卷〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0284007"><lem wit="【大】">一
<lb n="0284c12" ed="T"/>卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0284c13" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0284c14" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0284008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔開府…智〕三十三字－【宋】【元】【丙】【丁】，開府儀同三司＝唐【明】，〔開府儀同三司〕－【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0284008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿〕十二字－【宋】【元】【丙】【丁】，開府儀同三司＝唐【明】，〔開府儀同三司〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0284008"><lem wit="【大】">開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唐特進試鴻臚卿</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">特進試鴻臚卿</rdg></app><note n="0284009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔肅國…寺〕二十五字－【明】，〔肅國…智〕二十一字－【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0284009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒正號大廣智大興善寺〕二十五字－【明】，〔肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒正號大廣智〕二十一字－【宋】【元】【丙】【丁】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0284009"><lem wit="【大】">肅國
<lb n="0284c15" ed="T"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒
<lb n="0284c16" ed="T"/>正號大廣智大興善寺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【丙】【丁】【甲】【乙】">大興善寺</rdg></app>三藏沙門
<lb n="0284c17" ed="T"/><note n="0284010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（大廣智）＋不【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0284010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（大廣智）＋不【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0284010"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】">大廣智不</rdg></app>空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0284c18" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT18p0284c1801">金剛頂<note n="0284011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經瑜伽＝瑜伽經【宮】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0284011"><lem wit="【大】">經瑜伽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】【丙】【丁】">瑜伽經</rdg></app>有十萬偈十八會，初會名一
<lb n="0284c19" ed="T"/>切如來真實攝教王，有四大品：一名金剛界，
<lb n="0284c20" ed="T"/>二名降三世，三名遍調伏，四名一切義成就表
<lb n="0284c21" ed="T"/>四智印。於初品中有六曼<note n="0284012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">茶＝荼【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】下同</note><note n="0284012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">茶＝荼【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】下同</note><app n="0284012"><lem wit="【大】">茶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】">荼</rdg></app>羅，所謂金剛界
<lb n="0284c22" ed="T"/>大曼茶羅，并說毘盧遮那佛受用身，以五相
<lb n="0284c23" ed="T"/>現成等正覺<note n="0284013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔五相…達〕三十一字－【甲】</note><app n="0284013" cb:word-count="31"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">五相<note n="0284014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【乙】</note><app n="0284014"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>所謂通達本心、修菩提心、成金剛心、證金剛身、佛身圓滿，此則五智通達</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，
<lb n="0284c24" ed="T"/>成佛後以金剛三摩地現發，生三十七智，廣
<lb n="0284c25" ed="T"/>說曼<choice><corr>荼</corr><sic>茶</sic></choice>羅儀則，為弟子受速證菩薩地<note n="0284015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛地〕－【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0284015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛地〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0284015"><lem wit="【大】">佛地</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0284c26" ed="T"/>法。第二說陀羅尼曼茶羅，具三十七，此中聖
<lb n="0284c27" ed="T"/>眾皆住波羅蜜形，廣說入曼茶羅儀軌，為弟
<lb n="0284c28" ed="T"/>子受四種眼，說敬愛、鉤召、降伏、息災等儀軌。
<lb n="0284c29" ed="T"/>第三說微細金剛曼茶羅，亦具三十七聖眾，
<pb n="0285a" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0869.0285a"/>
<lb n="0285a01" ed="T"/>於金剛杵中畫，各持定印，廣說入曼茶羅儀
<lb n="0285a02" ed="T"/>軌，為弟子令心堪任、令心調柔、令心自在，說
<lb n="0285a03" ed="T"/>微細金剛三摩地，修四靜慮法、修四無量心
<lb n="0285a04" ed="T"/>及三解脫門。第四說一切如來廣大供養羯磨
<lb n="0285a05" ed="T"/>曼茶羅，亦具三十七，彼中聖眾，各持本<note n="0285001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">幖＝標【宋】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0285001"><lem wit="【大】">幖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【甲】【乙】">標</rdg></app>
<lb n="0285a06" ed="T"/>幟，供養而住，廣說入曼茶羅法，<note n="0285002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔為〕－【三】【宮】【丙】【丁】，為弟子＝互【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0285002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為弟子＝互【甲】【乙】，〔為〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0285002"><lem wit="【大】">為弟子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">互</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【丙】【丁】">弟子</rdg></app>說
<lb n="0285a07" ed="T"/>受十六大供養法，<note n="0285003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔說四…法〕八字－【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丁】</note><note n="0285003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔說四…法〕八字－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丁】</note><app n="0285003" cb:word-count="8"><lem wit="【大】">說四種祕密供養法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。第五
<lb n="0285a08" ed="T"/>說四印曼茶羅法，<note n="0285004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（為）＋弟【丙】</note><app n="0285004"><lem wit="【大】">弟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">為弟</rdg></app>子受四種速成就<note n="0285005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔法〕－【三】【宮】【丙】【丁】＊</note><note n="0285005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔法〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【丙】【丁】＊</note><app n="0285005"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，
<lb n="0285a09" ed="T"/>以此曼茶羅求悉地成就，<note n="0285006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔像〕－【丁】</note><app n="0285006"><lem wit="【大】">像</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>如上四曼茶羅
<lb n="0285a10" ed="T"/><note n="0285007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔中〕－【甲】</note><app n="0285007"><lem wit="【大】">中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>所求悉地，於此像前求成就。</p>
<lb n="0285a11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285a1101">第六說一印曼茶羅，若持毘盧遮那真言及
<lb n="0285a12" ed="T"/>金剛<note n="0285008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔薩埵〕－【丙】</note><app n="0285008"><lem wit="【大】">薩埵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>菩<note n="0285009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">薩＋（真言）【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0285009"><lem wit="【大】">薩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】">薩真言</rdg></app>具十七尊，餘皆具十三，亦
<lb n="0285a13" ed="T"/>說入曼茶羅儀，<note n="0285010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">與＝為【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0285010"><lem wit="【大】">與</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】">為</rdg></app>弟子受先行法，修集本尊
<lb n="0285a14" ed="T"/>三摩地。</p>
<lb n="0285a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285a1501">次說降三世大品，有六曼茶羅，如來成等正
<lb n="0285a16" ed="T"/>覺已，於須彌盧頂轉金剛界<note n="0285011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">輪＝轉【明】</note><app n="0285011"><lem wit="【大】">輪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">轉</rdg></app>已，與諸菩
<lb n="0285a17" ed="T"/>薩名號受職已，摩醯首羅等剛強難化，不可
<lb n="0285a18" ed="T"/>以寂靜法而受化。盡虛空遍法界一切如來
<lb n="0285a19" ed="T"/>異口同音，請以一百八名讚禮金剛薩埵。如
<lb n="0285a20" ed="T"/>是諸天不可以寂靜法而受化，<note n="0285012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔時金剛手菩薩受〕－【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0285012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔時金剛手菩薩受〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0285012"><lem wit="【大】">時金剛手菩
<lb n="0285a21" ed="T"/>薩受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>一切如來請<note n="0285013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝以【三】【宮】</note><note n="0285013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已＝以【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0285013"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">以</rdg></app>，即入<note n="0285014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悲＝忿【三】【宮】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0285014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悲＝忿【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0285014"><lem wit="【大】">悲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【丙】【丁】">忿</rdg></app>怒金剛三摩
<lb n="0285a22" ed="T"/>地，現大威德身，以種種方便調伏，乃至<note n="0285015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">命終＝至死【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丁】</note><note n="0285015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">命終＝至死【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丁】</note><app n="0285015"><lem wit="【大】">命
<lb n="0285a23" ed="T"/>終</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丁】">至死</rdg></app>。摩醯首羅死已，自見於下方過六十二恒
<lb n="0285a24" ed="T"/>河沙世界，名灰莊嚴，彼世界中成等正覺，名
<lb n="0285a25" ed="T"/>為怖畏自在王如來。執金剛菩薩以脚按<note n="0285016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＝上【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0285016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之＝上【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0285016"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】">上</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0285a26" ed="T"/>誦金剛壽命真言，復得蘇。既受化已，金剛薩
<lb n="0285a27" ed="T"/>埵則說大曼茶羅，引入諸天，受金剛名號諸
<lb n="0285a28" ed="T"/>天有五類。</p>
<lb n="0285a29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285a2901"><note n="0285017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（第一）＋居【三】【乙】【丙】【丁】，〔居上…后〕七十八字－【甲】</note><note n="0285017" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: a-->（第一）＋居【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】【丁】，〔居上…后〕七十八字－【甲】</note>居上界天王，摩醯首羅等無量諸天及后。</p>
<pb n="0285b" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0869.0285b"/>
<lb n="0285b01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285b0101">第二遊虛空諸天，日天子等無量諸天及后。</p>
<lb n="0285b02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285b0201">第三居虛空天，魔王等無量諸天及后。</p>
<lb n="0285b03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285b0301">第四地居天，<note n="0285018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">主＝生【乙】</note><app n="0285018"><lem wit="【大】">主</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">生</rdg></app>藏天等無量諸天及后。</p>
<lb n="0285b04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285b0401">第五地下嚩囉呬天等無量諸天及后。悉皆引
<lb n="0285b05" ed="T"/><note n="0285019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入已＝已入【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0285019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">入已＝已入【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0285019"><lem wit="【大】">入已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】">已入</rdg></app>，勅諸天建立諸曼茶羅，<note n="0285020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">汝＝法【乙】</note><app n="0285020"><lem wit="【大】">汝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">法</rdg></app>等赴會，所
<lb n="0285b06" ed="T"/>求一切悉<note n="0285021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔地〕－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0285021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔地〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0285021"><lem wit="【大】">地</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>皆與成辦，此等皆是外金剛部。</p>
<lb n="0285b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285b0701">第一說<note n="0285022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕－【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0285022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔大〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0285022"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>曼茶羅儀則，皆具三十七，說降伏
<lb n="0285b08" ed="T"/>法及修神通法。</p>
<lb n="0285b09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285b0901">第二說祕密曼茶羅，具三十七，說<note n="0285023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＋（入）【甲】</note><app n="0285023"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">引入</rdg></app>弟子
<lb n="0285b10" ed="T"/>儀，此中諸音聲及金剛歌舞。</p>
<lb n="0285b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285b1101">第三說<app type="star" corresp="#0285005"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>曼茶羅，具三十七，說引入弟子
<lb n="0285b12" ed="T"/>儀，此中說以慈悲喜捨，<note n="0285024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔作〕－【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0285024"><lem wit="【大】">作</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>阿毘遮嚕迦法，
<lb n="0285b13" ed="T"/>微細金剛調心<note n="0285025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">儀軌＝軌儀【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0285025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">儀軌＝軌儀【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0285025"><lem wit="【大】">儀軌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】">軌儀</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0285b14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285b1401">第四說羯磨曼茶羅，具三十七，說入曼茶羅
<lb n="0285b15" ed="T"/>儀，令弟子學護摩儀軌，於無量佛菩薩所，成
<lb n="0285b16" ed="T"/>廣大供養，速得悉地現前，說二十五種護摩
<lb n="0285b17" ed="T"/>爐隨類所求法。</p>
<lb n="0285b18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285b1801">第五說四印曼茶羅，具二十一，成就諸藥法
<lb n="0285b19" ed="T"/>等。已上<note n="0285026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">四＋（印）【甲】</note><app n="0285026"><lem wit="【大】">四</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">四印</rdg></app>曼茶羅中成就法，於此曼茶羅
<lb n="0285b20" ed="T"/><note n="0285027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔中成…羅〕九字－【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0285027" cb:word-count="9"><lem wit="【大】">中成就法於此曼茶羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>像前求。</p>
<lb n="0285b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285b2101">第六說一印曼茶羅，具十七，說引入弟子及
<lb n="0285b22" ed="T"/>先行法。</p><p xml:id="pT18p0285b2204" rend="inline"><note n="0285028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔次〕－【甲】</note><app n="0285028"><lem wit="【大】">次</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>為外金剛部眾，說四種曼茶羅，
<lb n="0285b23" ed="T"/>各說本真言、本印契獻佛。<note n="0285029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛＝已【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0285029"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">已</rdg></app>為說教勅大曼
<lb n="0285b24" ed="T"/>茶羅，具三十七，說引入弟子儀，說為弟子使
<lb n="0285b25" ed="T"/>役<note n="0285030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔外〕－【三】</note><note n="0285030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔外〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0285030"><lem wit="【大】">外</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>金剛部軌則，此中說大佛頂及光聚佛
<lb n="0285b26" ed="T"/>頂真言及契，亦通一字頂輪法。</p>
<lb n="0285b27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285b2701">次說第二教勅三昧耶曼茶羅，彼諸天后等
<lb n="0285b28" ed="T"/>各獻本真言，佛為說曼茶羅，具三十七，說為
<lb n="0285b29" ed="T"/>弟子說<note n="0285031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔修藥叉〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0285031"><lem wit="【大】">修藥叉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0285032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔藥〕－【三】</note><note n="0285032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔藥〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0285032"><lem wit="【大】">藥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>叉女法，廣說諸儀軌。</p>
<pb n="0285c" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0869.0285c"/>
<lb n="0285c01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285c0101">次第三說教勅法曼茶羅，諸天說真言獻佛，
<lb n="0285c02" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0285029"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">已</rdg></app>為彼等說曼茶羅，具三十七，說引入弟子
<lb n="0285c03" ed="T"/>儀，為弟子說諸天<note n="0285033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＝子【宮】</note><app n="0285033"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">子</rdg></app><note n="0285034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法＋（法）【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0285034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法＋（法）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0285034"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】">法法</rdg></app>印<note n="0285035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔已〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0285035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔已〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0285035"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，由此印不違
<lb n="0285c04" ed="T"/>越本誓。</p>
<lb n="0285c05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285c0501">次第四說教勅羯磨曼茶羅，具三十七，說引
<lb n="0285c06" ed="T"/>入<note n="0285036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">弟＝第【明】</note><app n="0285036"><lem wit="【大】">弟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">第</rdg></app>子儀。彼等諸天各說本真言，佛為說
<lb n="0285c07" ed="T"/>曼茶羅，說諸天<note n="0285037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔舞〕－【甲】</note><app n="0285037"><lem wit="【大】">舞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>儀，說成就諸事業速疾
<lb n="0285c08" ed="T"/>法。</p><p xml:id="pT18p0285c0802" rend="inline">次說遍調伏大品，有六種曼茶羅。</p>
<lb n="0285c09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285c0901">第<note n="0285038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一＋（說）【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0285038"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】">一說</rdg></app>大曼茶羅，具三十七，皆觀自在菩薩變
<lb n="0285c10" ed="T"/>現，說引入弟子儀，此中說十六種成就速疾
<lb n="0285c11" ed="T"/>神通三摩地儀。</p>
<lb n="0285c12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285c1201">第二說三昧<note n="0285039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耶＝邪【宮】＊</note><app n="0285039"><lem wit="【大】">耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">邪</rdg></app>曼茶羅，具三十七，皆觀自在
<lb n="0285c13" ed="T"/>菩薩變現，說引入弟子儀，此中說鉤召、敬愛
<lb n="0285c14" ed="T"/>十六種三摩地。</p>
<lb n="0285c15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285c1501">第三說法曼茶羅，具三十七，皆觀自在菩薩
<lb n="0285c16" ed="T"/>變現，說引入弟子儀，此中說修心及求智慧
<lb n="0285c17" ed="T"/>辯才法十六種。</p>
<lb n="0285c18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285c1801">第四說羯磨曼茶羅，具三十七，皆觀自在菩
<lb n="0285c19" ed="T"/>薩變現，說引<note n="0285040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔入〕－【三】</note><note n="0285040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔入〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0285040"><lem wit="【大】">入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>弟子儀，此中說蓮花部供養
<lb n="0285c20" ed="T"/>儀，及轉罪障報障、蓋纏業障法。</p>
<lb n="0285c21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285c2101">第五說蓮花部四印曼茶羅，具二十一，皆觀
<lb n="0285c22" ed="T"/>自在菩薩變現，說引入弟子儀，此中說成就，
<lb n="0285c23" ed="T"/><note n="0285041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔先行〕－【丁】</note><app n="0285041"><lem wit="【大】">先行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>法及成就<note n="0285042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔先行〕－【丙】</note><app n="0285042"><lem wit="【大】">先行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>如上四種曼茶羅法。</p>
<lb n="0285c24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0285c2401">第六說蓮花部<note n="0285043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">中＝印【三】【乙】，〔中〕－【甲】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0285043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">中＝印【宋】【元】【明】【乙】，〔中〕－【甲】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0285043"><lem wit="【大】">中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">印</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>一印曼茶羅，具十三，皆觀
<pb n="0286a" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0869.0286a"/>
<lb n="0286a01" ed="T"/>自在菩薩變現，說引入弟子儀，此中說修本
<lb n="0286a02" ed="T"/>尊法，通修世間出世間法。</p>
<lb n="0286a03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0286a0301">次說一切義成就大品中，有六曼茶羅。第一
<lb n="0286a04" ed="T"/>大曼茶羅，具三十七，此中說引入弟子儀，由
<lb n="0286a05" ed="T"/>入此曼茶羅，除貧匱業，說求豐財，求佛菩薩
<lb n="0286a06" ed="T"/>位及世間榮位。</p>
<lb n="0286a07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0286a0701">第二祕密三昧耶曼茶羅，具三十七，此中說
<lb n="0286a08" ed="T"/>引入弟子儀，說求伏藏法，速滿檀波羅蜜福
<lb n="0286a09" ed="T"/>德聚法。</p>
<lb n="0286a10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0286a1001">第三法曼茶羅，具三十七，此中說引入弟子
<lb n="0286a11" ed="T"/>儀，<note n="0286001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔說〕－【甲】</note><app n="0286001"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>寶部中修三摩地法，令心安住、令心
<lb n="0286a12" ed="T"/>堪任、令心調柔、令心自在，見虛空藏菩薩
<lb n="0286a13" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0285005"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0286a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0286a1401">第四羯磨曼茶羅，具三十七，此中說引入弟
<lb n="0286a15" ed="T"/>子儀，說加持掘伏藏事業法，并說寶部中廣
<lb n="0286a16" ed="T"/>大供養諸佛儀。</p>
<lb n="0286a17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0286a1701">第五四印曼茶羅，具二十一，說引入弟子儀，
<lb n="0286a18" ed="T"/>說修先行法，及<note n="0286002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">說＋（修）【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0286002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">說＋（修）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0286002"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】">說修</rdg></app>四曼茶羅中悉地法。</p>
<lb n="0286a19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0286a1901">第六一印曼茶羅，具十三，說引入弟子儀，說
<lb n="0286a20" ed="T"/><note n="0286003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔修〕－【甲】</note><app n="0286003"><lem wit="【大】">修</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>一尊法，及修諸藥等三摩地，皆是則彼婆
<lb n="0286a21" ed="T"/>伽梵執金剛虛空藏變化。次都說如前一一
<lb n="0286a22" ed="T"/>曼茶羅中，祕密助成方便散誦。次後<note n="0286004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">示＋（現）【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0286004"><lem wit="【大】">示</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】">示現</rdg></app>釋迦
<lb n="0286a23" ed="T"/>牟尼佛，降於閻浮提，變化身八相成道，皆是
<lb n="0286a24" ed="T"/>普賢菩薩幻化，一切如來還以一百八名，讚
<lb n="0286a25" ed="T"/>揚金剛薩埵。如是第一會。</p>
<lb n="0286a26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0286a2601">次說第二會，名一切如來祕密<note n="0286005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝主【元】【明】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0286005"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【丙】【丁】">主</rdg></app>瑜伽，於色
<lb n="0286a27" ed="T"/>究竟天說。具四大品，廣說<note n="0286006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔微細…說〕八字－【甲】</note><app n="0286006" cb:word-count="8"><lem wit="【大】">微細實相理，及
<lb n="0286a28" ed="T"/>廣說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>降摩醯首<note n="0286007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＋（天）【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0286007"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】【丁】">羅天</rdg></app>、<note n="0286008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔摩醯首羅〕－【三】【宮】【甲】</note><note n="0286008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔摩醯首羅〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】</note><app n="0286008"><lem wit="【大】">摩醯首羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0286009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔天〕－【乙】</note><app n="0286009"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，以偈與金
<lb n="0286a29" ed="T"/>剛菩薩酬答。</p>
<pb n="0286b" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0869.0286b"/>
<lb n="0286b01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0286b0101">次說第三會，名一切教集瑜伽，於法界宮殿
<lb n="0286b02" ed="T"/>說。一切如來異口同音，問金剛薩埵菩薩一
<lb n="0286b03" ed="T"/>百八問，金剛薩埵菩薩一一答。此經中說大
<lb n="0286b04" ed="T"/>曼茶羅五部，一一部中五曼茶羅，各具三十
<lb n="0286b05" ed="T"/>七，都成一大曼茶羅。一一尊各各說四印，所
<lb n="0286b06" ed="T"/>謂大印、三昧耶印、法印、羯磨印，各說成就
<lb n="0286b07" ed="T"/>法，此經中說一百<note n="0286010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝三【三】</note><note n="0286010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二＝三【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0286010"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">三</rdg></app>十五種護摩爐，一一爐
<lb n="0286b08" ed="T"/>所求各異。</p>
<lb n="0286b09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0286b0901">次說第四會，名降三<note n="0286011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世＝母【宮】</note><app n="0286011"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">母</rdg></app>金剛瑜伽，於須彌盧
<lb n="0286b10" ed="T"/>頂說。金剛藏等八大菩薩，一一尊各說四種
<lb n="0286b11" ed="T"/>曼茶羅，初會說降伏摩醯首羅及<note n="0286012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸＝說【三】【宮】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0286012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸＝說【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0286012"><lem wit="【大】">諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【丙】【丁】">說</rdg></app>天<note n="0286013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入＝人【三】</note><note n="0286013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">入＝人【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0286013"><lem wit="【大】">入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">人</rdg></app>
<lb n="0286b12" ed="T"/>曼茶羅<note n="0286014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">授＝受【三】【宮】＊【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0286014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">授＝受【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0286014"><lem wit="【大】">授</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】">受</rdg></app>職<note n="0286015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔位〕－【三】【宮】【乙】</note><note n="0286015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔位〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【乙】</note><app n="0286015"><lem wit="【大】">位</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0286014"><lem wit="【大】">授</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">受</rdg></app>名號四種曼茶羅，所謂
<lb n="0286b13" ed="T"/>大曼茶羅、三昧耶曼茶羅、法曼茶羅、羯磨曼
<lb n="0286b14" ed="T"/>茶羅，及一<note n="0286016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一＝切【三】</note><note n="0286016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一＝切【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0286016"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">切</rdg></app>尊說引入弟子儀及成就法，
<lb n="0286b15" ed="T"/>後都<note n="0286017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔說〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0286017"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0286018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0286018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔諸〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0286018"><lem wit="【大】">諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>尊三昧<app type="star" corresp="#0285039"><lem wit="【大】">耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">邪</rdg></app>結印次第，及說祕密
<lb n="0286b16" ed="T"/>禁戒及祕密修行。</p>
<lb n="0286b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0286b1701">第五會名世間出世間金剛瑜伽，於波羅奈
<lb n="0286b18" ed="T"/>國空界<note n="0286019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">中＋（說）【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0286019"><lem wit="【大】">中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】">中說</rdg></app>，略說五佛曼茶羅，及諸菩薩諸外
<lb n="0286b19" ed="T"/>金剛部曼茶羅，一一曼茶羅具四種，各說引
<lb n="0286b20" ed="T"/>入弟子儀及求悉地法。</p>
<lb n="0286b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0286b2101">第六會名大安樂不空三昧耶真實瑜伽，於
<lb n="0286b22" ed="T"/>他化自在天宮說。此經中說普賢菩薩曼茶
<lb n="0286b23" ed="T"/>羅，次說毘盧遮那曼茶羅，次後說金剛藏等，
<lb n="0286b24" ed="T"/>至金剛拳菩薩及外金剛部，說般若理趣。一
<lb n="0286b25" ed="T"/>一尊具說四種曼茶羅，各說引入弟子儀，授
<lb n="0286b26" ed="T"/>理趣般若波羅蜜多<app type="star" corresp="#0285005"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>及<note n="0286020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝授【三】【宮】【丙】【丁】＊</note><note n="0286020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受＝授【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【丙】【丁】＊</note><app n="0286020"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【丙】【丁】">授</rdg></app>四種印法，<note n="0286021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">品＋（品）【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0286021"><lem wit="【大】">品</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】">品品</rdg></app>
<lb n="0286b27" ed="T"/>中各說求世間出世間悉地法。</p>
<lb n="0286b28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0286b2801">第七會名普賢瑜伽，於普賢菩薩宮殿中說。
<lb n="0286b29" ed="T"/><note n="0286022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔此經中說〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】，〔此經〕－【宮】</note><note n="0286022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔此經中說〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】，〔此經〕－【宮】</note><app n="0286022"><lem wit="【大】">此經中說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">中說</rdg></app>普賢菩薩等，至金剛拳菩薩及
<pb n="0286c" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0869.0286c"/>
<lb n="0286c01" ed="T"/>外金剛部，一一尊各說四種曼茶羅，說引入
<lb n="0286c02" ed="T"/>弟子儀，說受四種印，修世間出世間悉地。此
<lb n="0286c03" ed="T"/>經中說修行人<note n="0286023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無＝元【元】＊</note><app n="0286023"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">元</rdg></app>時<app type="star" corresp="#0286023"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">元</rdg></app>方，不依世間禁戒，
<lb n="0286c04" ed="T"/>以菩提心為先，無為戒為本。</p>
<lb n="0286c05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0286c0501">第八會名勝初瑜伽，於普賢宮殿說。普賢菩
<lb n="0286c06" ed="T"/>薩等，至外金剛部，各各說四種曼茶羅，說實
<lb n="0286c07" ed="T"/>相理，及分別諸曼茶羅儀則，稍廣於第七會，
<lb n="0286c08" ed="T"/>說大略同。</p>
<lb n="0286c09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0286c0901">第九會名一切佛集會拏吉尼戒網瑜伽，於真
<lb n="0286c10" ed="T"/>言宮殿<note n="0286024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔說〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0286024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔說〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0286024"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。此中說立自身為本尊瑜伽，訶身
<lb n="0286c11" ed="T"/>外<note n="0286025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">主＝至【元】【明】，立【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0286025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">主＝至【元】【明】，＝立【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0286025"><lem wit="【大】">主</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">至</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】">立</rdg></app>形像瑜伽者，廣說實相理，并說五部根
<lb n="0286c12" ed="T"/>源，并說瑜伽法具九味，所謂華麗<note n="0286026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔金剛薩埵〕－【甲】</note><app n="0286026"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">金剛薩埵</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>、勇健
<lb n="0286c13" ed="T"/><note n="0286027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔毘盧遮那〕－【甲】</note><app n="0286027"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">毘盧遮那</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>、大悲<note n="0286028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔持金剛〕－【甲】</note><app n="0286028"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">持金剛</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>、喜笑<note n="0286029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔觀自在〕－【甲】</note><app n="0286029"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">觀自在</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>、瞋怒<note n="0286030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔金剛光〕－【甲】</note><app n="0286030"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">金剛光</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>、恐怖<note n="0286031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔降三世〕－【甲】</note><app n="0286031"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">降三
<lb n="0286c14" ed="T"/>世</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>、厭患<note n="0286032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔釋迦牟尼佛〕－【甲】</note><app n="0286032"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">釋迦牟尼佛</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>、奇特<note n="0286033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔金剛笑〕－【甲】</note><app n="0286033"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">金剛笑</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>、寂靜<note n="0286034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔瑜伽中毘盧遮那〕－【甲】</note><app n="0286034"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">瑜伽中毘盧遮那</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。說普賢
<lb n="0286c15" ed="T"/>菩薩等，至金剛拳，各說四種曼茶羅，及引入
<lb n="0286c16" ed="T"/>弟子儀，及<app type="star" corresp="#0286020"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【丙】【丁】">授</rdg></app>四種印，并說五部中歌讚舞儀。</p>
<lb n="0286c17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0286c1701">第十會名大三昧耶瑜伽，於法界宮殿說。普
<lb n="0286c18" ed="T"/>賢菩薩等，至金剛拳<note n="0286035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔菩薩〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0286035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔菩薩〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0286035"><lem wit="【大】">菩薩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>十六<note n="0286036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕－【甲】</note><app n="0286036"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>菩薩，各
<lb n="0286c19" ed="T"/>各說四種曼茶羅，說引入弟子儀，<app type="star" corresp="#0286020"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【丙】【丁】">授</rdg></app>四種印
<lb n="0286c20" ed="T"/>法。此中說偈云：</p>
<lb n="0286c21" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT18p0286c2101" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「愚童覆無智，</l><l>不知此理趣，</l>
<lb n="0286c22" ed="T"/><l>餘處而求佛，</l><l>不悟此處有。</l>
<lb n="0286c23" ed="T"/><l>十方世界中，</l><l>餘處不可得，</l>
<lb n="0286c24" ed="T"/><l>心自為等覺，</l><l>餘處不說佛。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0286c25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0286c2501">第十一會名大乘現證瑜伽，於阿迦尼吒天
<lb n="0286c26" ed="T"/>說。毘盧遮那佛等，<note n="0286037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">至金剛＝金剛至【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0286037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">至金剛＝金剛至【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0286037"><lem wit="【大】">至金剛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】">金剛至</rdg></app>毘首羯磨菩薩，
<lb n="0286c27" ed="T"/>及八大供養四攝出生同真實攝瑜伽，一一
<lb n="0286c28" ed="T"/>尊具四種曼茶羅四種印，廣說實相<note n="0286038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔理〕－【甲】</note><app n="0286038"><lem wit="【大】">理</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>心建
<lb n="0286c29" ed="T"/>立曼茶羅儀則。</p>
<pb n="0287a" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0869.0287a"/>
<lb n="0287a01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0287a0101">第十二會名三昧耶最勝瑜伽，於空界菩提
<lb n="0287a02" ed="T"/>場說。毘盧遮那等四部中上首菩薩，金剛拳
<lb n="0287a03" ed="T"/><note n="0287001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">等＋（二十）【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0287001"><lem wit="【大】">等</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】【丁】">等二十</rdg></app><note n="0287002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（第）＋八【三】【宮】</note><note n="0287002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（第）＋八【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0287002"><lem wit="【大】">八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">第八</rdg></app>菩薩及外金剛部，各各說四種曼荼
<lb n="0287a04" ed="T"/>羅四印等<note n="0287003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔八〕－【三】</note><note n="0287003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔八〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0287003"><lem wit="【大】">八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。此經中，於自身上建立曼荼
<lb n="0287a05" ed="T"/>羅，說自身本尊瑜伽，廣說阿字門通達於染
<lb n="0287a06" ed="T"/>淨，有為無為無礙。</p>
<lb n="0287a07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0287a0701">第十三會名大三昧<app type="star" corresp="#0285039"><lem wit="【大】">耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">邪</rdg></app>真實瑜伽，於金剛界
<lb n="0287a08" ed="T"/>曼荼羅道場說。十方一<note n="0287004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">切＋（諸）【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0287004"><lem wit="【大】">切</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】">切諸</rdg></app>佛異口同音，請金
<lb n="0287a09" ed="T"/>剛薩埵，<note n="0287005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0287005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0287005"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惟</rdg></app>願說三昧耶真實教法，我等先已
<lb n="0287a10" ed="T"/>受訖，<app type="star" corresp="#0287005"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惟</rdg></app>願金剛薩埵為諸菩薩。<note n="0287006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">既授＝說得【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0287006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">既授＝說得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0287006"><lem wit="【大】">既授</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】">說得</rdg></app>請已，
<lb n="0287a11" ed="T"/>說普賢菩薩十七字真言，說適悅不空曼荼
<lb n="0287a12" ed="T"/>羅，具十七，亦說四種曼荼羅，說一百八道契，
<lb n="0287a13" ed="T"/>說通求世間出世間悉地。隨此諸菩薩及外
<lb n="0287a14" ed="T"/>金剛部，各各說本曼荼羅本真言本<note n="0287007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">契印＝印契【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0287007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">契印＝印契【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0287007"><lem wit="【大】">契印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】">印契</rdg></app>竟，
<lb n="0287a15" ed="T"/>普賢菩<note n="0287008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">薩＋（復）【丁】</note><app n="0287008"><lem wit="【大】">薩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】">薩復</rdg></app>說祕密中曼荼羅十七尊支分，各
<lb n="0287a16" ed="T"/>復入本尊身，共成五尊，同居一蓮花臺，說一
<lb n="0287a17" ed="T"/>字真言，從眼口及一切支分變異即成印，但
<lb n="0287a18" ed="T"/>住大印結羯磨印，不待先行不<note n="0287009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">籍＝藉【三】</note><note n="0287009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">籍＝藉【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0287009"><lem wit="【大】">籍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">藉</rdg></app>結護加持，
<lb n="0287a19" ed="T"/>亦不假迎請，宿業罪障不能<note n="0287010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陵＝凌【三】</note><note n="0287010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">陵＝凌【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0287010"><lem wit="【大】">陵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">凌</rdg></app>逼，亦不障礙
<lb n="0287a20" ed="T"/>速疾成就。</p>
<lb n="0287a21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0287a2101">第十四會名如來三昧耶真實瑜伽，此經中
<lb n="0287a22" ed="T"/>普賢菩薩十六大菩薩，四攝成一身，說四種
<lb n="0287a23" ed="T"/>曼荼羅四印，廣說五部互圓融，如來部即金
<lb n="0287a24" ed="T"/>剛，蓮花部即寶部，互相涉入，法界即真如，般
<lb n="0287a25" ed="T"/>若即實際，於假施設有異，於本即一體。次普
<lb n="0287a26" ed="T"/>賢後諸菩薩及外金剛部，各各說本真言、本
<lb n="0287a27" ed="T"/>曼荼羅、本印契。</p>
<lb n="0287a28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0287a2801">第十五會名祕密集會瑜伽，於祕密處說，所
<lb n="0287a29" ed="T"/>謂喻<note n="0287011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔師〕－【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0287011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔師〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0287011"><lem wit="【大】">師</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>婆伽處說，號般若波羅蜜宮。此中說
<pb n="0287b" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0869.0287b"/>
<lb n="0287b01" ed="T"/>教法壇印契真言，住禁戒，<note n="0287012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">似＝以【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0287012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">似＝以【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0287012"><lem wit="【大】">似</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】">以</rdg></app>如世間貪染相
<lb n="0287b02" ed="T"/>應語。會中除蓋障菩薩等從座而起，禮佛白
<lb n="0287b03" ed="T"/>言：「世尊大人不應出麁言雜染相應語。」佛言：
<lb n="0287b04" ed="T"/>「汝等清淨相應語，有何相狀？我之此語，加持
<lb n="0287b05" ed="T"/>文字，應化緣方<note n="0287013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＋（語）【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0287013"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】">便語</rdg></app>，引入佛道，亦無相狀，成
<lb n="0287b06" ed="T"/>大利益，汝等不應生疑。」從此廣說實相三摩
<lb n="0287b07" ed="T"/>地，諸菩薩各各說四種曼荼羅四印。</p>
<lb n="0287b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0287b0801">第十六會名無二平等瑜伽，於法界宮說。毘
<lb n="0287b09" ed="T"/>盧遮那佛及諸菩薩并外金剛部等，各各<note n="0287014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔說〕－【三】</note><note n="0287014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔說〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0287014"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0287b10" ed="T"/>四種曼荼羅，具四印，此中說生死涅槃、世間
<lb n="0287b11" ed="T"/>出世間、自他平等無二<note n="0287015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">種＝動【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0287015"><lem wit="【大】">種</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】">動</rdg></app>心，舉<note n="0287016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">目＝自【三】</note><note n="0287016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">目＝自【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0287016"><lem wit="【大】">目</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">自</rdg></app><note n="0287017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聲＝身【明】</note><app n="0287017"><lem wit="【大】">聲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">身</rdg></app>香味
<lb n="0287b12" ed="T"/>觸雜染思慮住亂心<note n="0287018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（皆）＋無【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0287018"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】">皆無</rdg></app>二，同真如法界，皆成
<lb n="0287b13" ed="T"/>一切佛身。</p>
<lb n="0287b14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0287b1401">第十七會名如虛空瑜伽，住實際宮殿說。毘
<lb n="0287b15" ed="T"/>盧遮那佛、普賢菩薩及外金剛部，一一說四
<lb n="0287b16" ed="T"/>種曼荼羅，具四種印。此中修行者，與一一尊
<lb n="0287b17" ed="T"/>相應，皆量同虛空法身相應，<note n="0287019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">離＝利【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0287019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">離＝利【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0287019"><lem wit="【大】">離</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】">利</rdg></app>一切萬物，
<lb n="0287b18" ed="T"/>法體光明量同虛空無來無去。此經中說虛
<lb n="0287b19" ed="T"/>空三摩地相應法。</p>
<lb n="0287b20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0287b2001">第十八會名金剛寶冠瑜伽，於第四靜慮天。
<lb n="0287b21" ed="T"/><note n="0287020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（說）＋金【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0287020"><lem wit="【大】">金</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】">說金</rdg></app>剛薩埵菩薩<note n="0287021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔請〕－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0287021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔請〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0287021"><lem wit="【大】">請</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>佛，為<note n="0287022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大梵＝梵大【明】</note><app n="0287022"><lem wit="【大】">大梵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">梵大</rdg></app>天娑訶世界
<lb n="0287b22" ed="T"/>主說五部瑜伽曼荼羅引入弟子儀，具三十
<lb n="0287b23" ed="T"/>七，亦說四種曼荼羅，具四印。下至外金剛部，
<lb n="0287b24" ed="T"/>為弟子<app type="star" corresp="#0286020"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【丙】【丁】">授</rdg></app>學心念誦，於月輪上<note n="0287023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">右＝有【三】【宮】</note><note n="0287023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">右＝有【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0287023"><lem wit="【大】">右</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">有</rdg></app>旋列真
<lb n="0287b25" ed="T"/>言字，<note n="0287024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">注＝住【三】【宮】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0287024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">注＝住【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0287024"><lem wit="【大】">注</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【乙】【丙】【丁】">住</rdg></app>心於一一字，實相理相應，<note n="0287025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">周＝用【三】</note><note n="0287025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">周＝用【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0287025"><lem wit="【大】">周</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">用</rdg></app>而復
<lb n="0287b26" ed="T"/>始，亦通成就世間出世間悉地，不假持珠遍
<lb n="0287b27" ed="T"/>數以為劑限，但證理門心不散動，住本尊瑜
<lb n="0287b28" ed="T"/>伽為限。<note n="0287026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔此經中〕－【三】【宮】【乙】</note><note n="0287026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔此經中〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【乙】</note><app n="0287026"><lem wit="【大】">此經中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>微細說不成就二十種相，及
<lb n="0287b29" ed="T"/>說隣近悉地多種相。</p><p xml:id="pT18p0287b2909" rend="inline">瑜伽教十八會，或四千
<pb n="0287c" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0869.0287c"/>
<lb n="0287c01" ed="T"/>頌或五千頌或七千頌，都成十萬頌，具五部
<lb n="0287c02" ed="T"/>四種曼荼羅四印，具三十七尊，一一部具三
<lb n="0287c03" ed="T"/>十七，乃至一尊成三十七，亦具四曼荼羅四
<lb n="0287c04" ed="T"/>印，互相涉入，如帝釋網珠光明交映展轉無
<lb n="0287c05" ed="T"/>限。修行者善達此瑜伽中大意，如遍照佛，一
<lb n="0287c06" ed="T"/>一身分、一一毛孔、一一相、一一隨<note n="0287027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">形＝刑【明】</note><app n="0287027"><lem wit="【大】">形</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">刑</rdg></app>好、一
<lb n="0287c07" ed="T"/>一福德資糧、一一智慧資糧，住於果位，演說
<lb n="0287c08" ed="T"/>瑜伽二乘不共佛法，說曼荼羅三昧<note n="0287028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耶＝邪【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0287028"><lem wit="【大】">耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">邪</rdg></app>法門
<lb n="0287c09" ed="T"/>事業，量同虛空，證者如上所說，各各分劑<note n="0287029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">各＋（各）【明】</note><app n="0287029"><lem wit="【大】">各</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">各各</rdg></app>
<lb n="0287c10" ed="T"/>不雜亂，圓證四身，所謂自性身、受用身、變化
<lb n="0287c11" ed="T"/>身、等流身，是能<note n="0287030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">頓作＝作頓【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0287030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頓作＝作頓【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0287030"><lem wit="【大】">頓<note n="0287031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔作〕－【丁】</note><app n="0287031"><lem wit="【大】">作</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】">作頓</rdg></app>利樂一切有情、諸菩薩
<lb n="0287c12" ed="T"/>聲聞緣覺及諸外道，<note n="0287032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">名＋（為）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0287032"><lem wit="【大】">名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">名為</rdg></app>瑜伽金剛<note n="0287033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乘教＝一乘教王【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0287033"><lem wit="【大】">乘教</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】【丁】">一乘教王</rdg></app>法。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0287c13" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>金剛頂瑜伽<note n="0287034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔經〕－【宋】【元】【甲】</note><app n="0287034"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>十八會指<note n="0287035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">歸＋（一卷）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0287035"><lem wit="【大】">歸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">歸一卷</rdg></app><note n="0287036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">丙本奧朱書及丁本曰右十八會指歸一卷延寶八庚申年十月十六日以高麗國印本校合了，貞享三丙寅年五月朔夜校了淨嚴四十八載，丙本亦有此文兩本奧墨書曰元祿十五年十二月廿四日以和上御本再校了尊教</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0287c14" ed="T"/><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pT18p0287c1401"><note n="0287037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔金剛…卷〕九字－【三】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><note n="0287037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔金剛…卷〕九字－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】</note><app n="0287037" cb:word-count="9"><lem wit="【大】">金剛頂瑜伽指歸一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【甲】【乙】【丙】【丁】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p></cb:div>
